ðŸ”§ Tools for Today
Tool/Concept	       Description
open()	               Open files in different modes (r, w, a)
.read()	               Read the full content of a file
.readline()     	   Read one line at a time
.write()	           Write data to a file (overwrite)
.close()	           Close file manually
with open(...)	       Auto-close files (preferred method)
try/except(Optional)   Handle file not found errors